data.description: A must see, kid friendly 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home.  Beautiful crown molding is sure to catch your eye as you enter into both the living room and family room. Open kitchen and living space dawns the warmth of natural light. New flooring in the half bath, kitchen, family room and laundry room.  Retreat upstairs to the spacious master bedroom with vaulted ceiling and built in mantel. Enjoy the french doors to the bathroom as you walk through into the remodeled organized closet. Built in desk with shelves. Perfect for home office.  3 additional bedrooms await your attention.  One which includes a view overlooking the large backyard with privacy fence, play equipment and fire pit. All appliances are included.
